title: JUL 15, 2022 - SECRETIVE CHINESE OLIGARCH BUYS 140,000 ACRES OF LAND IN TEXAS NEAR LAUGHLIN AIR FORCE BASE
description:
NATIONAL SECURITY THREAT: a secretive Chinese oligarch purchased 140,000 acres of Texas land near Laughlin Air Force Base to build a wind farm - or so he claims. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez (AOC) theorizes that federal law enforcement, including the Capitol Police, aided in the January 6th storming of the Capitol, making the event an inside job. The NIH and the CDC have an employee exodus due to low morale brought on by ‘bad science’ regarding the Covid vaccine in five-year-olds. After a trip to Ukraine, Malcolm Nance declares that the conservative movement is an insurgency, and that ‘we may have to fight’ our neighbors. 



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
